events.name: South Carolina Gamecocks at Georgia Bulldogs

headlines.description: Aaron Murray threw for 309 yards and four touchdowns, Georgia's beleaguered defense finally came up with a stop, and the 11th-ranked Bulldogs defeated No. 6 South Carolina 41-30 on Saturday for an early edge in the Southeastern Conference East.

events.name: Sam Houston State Bearkats at Texas A&M Aggies

events.name: Eastern Kentucky Colonels at Louisville Cardinals

events.name: UAB Blazers at LSU Tigers

headlines.description: Zach Mettenberger passed for an LSU single-game record five touchdowns, receiver Odell Beckham Jr. scored one of his four touchdowns on a 100-yard field goal return, and the ninth-ranked Tigers overwhelmed UAB 56-17 on Saturday night.

events.name: Florida Gators at Miami Hurricanes
